<li id="cite_note-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C04EFDF163AF933A25751C1A9649C8B63&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=1">ARTS IN AMERICA; Here's to Disco, It Never Could Say Goodbye</a>, The New York Times, December 10, 2002</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.jahsonic.com/VinceAletti.html">Vince Aletti (1940 – )</a>, Excerpt from first article about disco</span></li>
